        <Parent_String>candlesticks [300037588], candleholders [300037583], candles and candleholders [300179872], lighting devices by form [300179870], lighting devices [300037581], lighting equipment [300428218], furnishings by form or function [300037342], furnishings (works) [300037336], Furnishings (hierarchy name) [300037335], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
